<t>CREATE TABLE WasteCollection (
    collection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    collection_date DATE,
    location_id INT,
    collected_weight DECIMAL
);


CREATE TABLE WasteType (
    type_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50)
);


CREATE TABLE WasteDisposal (
    disposal_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    disposal_date DATE,
    disposal_location INT,
    disposal_method VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_history (collection_id INT PRIMARY KEY, bin_id INT REFERENCES waste_bins(bin_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, collection_date DATE NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_locations (location_id INT PRIMARY KEY, location_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, location_address VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, collection_day VARCHAR(10));

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_schedule (schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY, location_id INT REFERENCES waste_collection_locations(location_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, collection_time TIME NOT NULL, collection_frequency VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL);</t><s>insert into waste_collection_locations (location_id, location_name, location_address, collection_day) values (1, 'location a', 'address a', 'monday') on conflict (location_id) do update set location_name = 'location a', location_address = 'address a', collection_day = 'monday';</s>

CREATE TABLE waste_bins (bin_id INT PRIMARY KEY, bin_type_id INT REFERENCES waste_bin_types(bin_type_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, location_id INT REFERENCES waste_collection_locations(location_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, last_collection_date DATE, is_full BOOLEAN NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_history (collection_id INT PRIMARY KEY, bin_id INT REFERENCES waste_bins(bin_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, collection_date DATE NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_locations (location_id INT PRIMARY KEY, location_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, location_address VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, collection_day VARCHAR(10));

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_schedule (schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY, location_id INT REFERENCES waste_collection_locations(location_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, collection_time TIME NOT NULL, collection_frequency VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL);</t><s>INSERT INTO waste_collection_locations (location_id, location_name, location_address, collection_day) VALUES (2, 'Location B', 'Address B', 'Wednesday') ON CONFLICT (location_id) DO UPDATE SET location_name = 'Location B', location_address = 'Address B', collection_day = 'Wednesday';</s>

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_schedule (schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY, location_id INT REFERENCES waste_collection_locations(location_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, collection_time TIME NOT NULL, collection_frequency VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_history (collection_id INT PRIMARY KEY, bin_id INT REFERENCES waste_bins(bin_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, collection_date DATE NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_locations (location_id INT PRIMARY KEY, location_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, location_address VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, collection_day VARCHAR(10));</t><s>insert into waste_collection_locations (location_id, location_name, location_address, collection_day) values (3, 'location c', 'address c', 'friday') on conflict (location_id) do update set location_name = 'location c', location_address = 'address c', collection_day = 'friday';</s>

CREATE TABLE waste_bins (bin_id INT PRIMARY KEY, bin_type_id INT REFERENCES waste_bin_types(bin_type_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, location_id INT REFERENCES waste_collection_locations(location_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, last_collection_date DATE, is_full BOOLEAN NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE waste_bin_types (bin_type_id INT PRIMARY KEY, bin_type_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, capacity DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_locations (location_id INT PRIMARY KEY, location_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, location_address VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, collection_day VARCHAR(10));

CREATE TABLE waste_collection_schedule (schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY, location_id INT REFERENCES waste_collection_locations(location_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, collection_time TIME NOT NULL, collection_frequency VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL);</t><s>INSERT INTO waste_collection_locations (location_id, location_name, location_address, collection_day) VALUES (3, 'Location C', 'Address C', 'Friday') ON CONFLICT (location_id) DO UPDATE SET location_name = 'Location C', location_address = 'Address C', collection_day = 'Friday';</s>
